column5: Mike this notes for you.  This was the only fish in the system, im pretty sure the rest are headed out your way attracted by the magic of the lamiglass
For me? I sold the Lami to Fidel so all the mojo is his now.  Nice fishy.
no man the magic ain't his when we go fishing, its must of transferred to your new stick.  we'll all have to plan a trip to clear this up for once and for all.
found in a local trib only known to u and i. You'll have to check it after work on a regular basis
I thought those rocks looked familiar!!
